      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that reflects meticulous stewardship. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been preserved to ensure a driving experience that is indistinguishable from its original delivery state. For the discerning buyer seeking a superlative example of this model, this offering represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
