    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with the upkeep, so the interior is spotless and the paint still has that incredible deep shine. It drives like an absolute dream\u2014smooth, quiet, and plenty of pep. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s essentially brand new and ready for its next adventure, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
