    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in breathtaking showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and entirely free of creases or wear. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is peerless, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy at authorized service centers. Complete service records, both original keys, and the factory window sticker are included. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
      "price": 48500.0,
