    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of the 996.2 wide-body aesthetic and mechanical refinement. Powered by a naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, the engine delivers seamless power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is exceptionally tight, benefiting from the factory-spec AWD system and sport-tuned suspension that ensures neutral handling and immense mechanical grip. Key preventative maintenance is fully documented, including a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal, ensuring the integrity of the powertrain. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors, providing fade-free deceleration. Free of any fluid leaks or vacuum issues, this collector-grade 911 offers a visceral, analog driving experience in an uncompromising state of preservation.",
